This is the program to get latest tweets in last 7 days.

Install the following gems by running this instruction from your terminal. 

gem install twitter

gem install jumpstart_auth

to run this program

Invoke irb (Interactive Ruby or irb is an interactive programming environment that comes with Ruby.),type irb in the terminal.

run following commands

load './jstwitter.rb'

gs twitter_handle

for ex. gs mailtorupalik

Output : all the tweets in last 7 days from today's date.

press q to exit.
